    "content": "Native plan-node completion must honor successful validation outcomes correlated directly to the node id, because MCP commonly uses a native node id as the current task while recording `test_ran` and `fix_validated` events with no anchors. If completion logic only accepts anchor-matched evidence or real coordination-task ids, `plan_node_update` can reject completion even after the exact required validations were run and recorded.",
